c1","tid":611864,"uid":86841,"like":12,"dislike":89,"score":-77,"quote":{"pid":"fb0f44fd26a019f3bf0034fac3cfe1de153c8217","tid":611864,"uid":124899,"like":22,"dislike":161,"score":-139,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"就好似美國無錂鏡計畫咁。<br />\n<br />\ngoogle map日撚日提你幾點返工放工。搭乜車。<br />\ngoogle fit連你行過去邊都記錄低。<br />\n<br />\n真係百步笑五十步。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"【密室命案】內地律師身中30刀亡　公安堅稱自殺 　網民：鬼才信<br />\n撰文：李納德<br />\n2018-02-28 19:01<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-03-13 15:27<br />\n<br />\n內地發生離奇命案！一名律師被發現身中30多刀死在家中，但屋內門窗完好，無明顯打鬥痕跡，更離奇的是內地公安排除他殺可能，斷定律師自殺。死者家屬無法接受判決，向當地公安請願，但當局覆檢後維持原判。事件曝光後震驚網民，有人直言：「自己捅了自己30多刀，可能嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/163802/%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%AD30%E5%88%80%E4%BA%A1-%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%A0%85%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%AC%BC%E6%89%8D%E4%BF%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F163802%2F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD30%25E5%2588%2580%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25A0%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E6%2589%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d6ed1851\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/163802/%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%AD30%E5%88%80%E4%BA%A1-%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%A0%85%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%AC%BC%E6%89%8D%E4%BF%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n湖南衡阳公安局女子坠楼事件<br />\n2010年10月12日11時8分，網友在紅網論壇裡發帖：&ldquo;昨天衡陽市公安局為什麼有人跳樓？&rdquo;隨後，就有網友留言說：&ldquo;我親眼目睹跳樓整個過程，這女人在窗邊到跳樓大概有將近20分鐘的時間。自始至終沒有1個公安局的人出來採取任何預防措施，在這女人跳樓以後，許多警察出來了，不想多說&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n網友說：先從樓上掉下兩條女褲，一個皮包後，發現該女子坐在公安局7樓窗台上哭喊著：&ldquo;我爸爸！我爸爸！&rdquo;持續了近20分鐘，當時有好幾位警察在一樓現場，但並未採取有效措施，直至慘案發生&hellip;&hellip;當時有記者趕到現場拍攝，還被該局工作人員搶走設備&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/10%C2%B711%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97%E8%A1%A1%E9%98%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9D%A0%E6%A5%BC%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F10%25C2%25B711%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E9%2598%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%259D%25A0%25E6%25A5%25BC%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c94632c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/10%C2%B711%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97%E8%A1%A1%E9%98%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9D%A0%E6%A5%BC%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n大把例子"},{"pid":"0bf4b99b498712a21530dc3f39346d2b6e7a8e9c","tid":611864,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5ba6c7ac7efa68b05681caad8654469f1e0617","tid":611864,"uid":66618,"like":118,"dislike":12,"score":106,"quote":{"pid":"fb0f44fd26a019f3bf0034fac3cfe1de153c8217","tid":611864,"uid":124899,"like":22,"dislike":161,"score":-139,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"就好似美國無錂鏡計畫咁。<br />\n<br />\ngoogle map日撚日提你幾點返工放工。搭乜車。<br />\ngoogle fit連你行過去邊都記錄低。<br />\n<br />\n真係百步笑五十步。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"身有屎先會怕美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"好人好者怕咩比美國追蹤?"},{"pid":"5f1d8b0de96915a24ad93eae8820279ff5f59c19","tid":611864,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e5ba6c7ac7efa68b05681caad8654469f1e0617","tid":611864,"uid":66618,"like":118,"dislike":12,"score":106,"quote":{"pid":"fb0f44fd26a019f3bf0034fac3cfe1de153c8217","tid":611864,"uid":124899,"like":22,"dislike":161,"score":